WEBVTT


00:00:00.160 --> 00:00:01.280
Hi, I'm Grace.

00:00:01.280 --> 00:00:02.200
I'm a homemaker,

00:00:02.200 --> 00:00:04.600
wife and mother who loves the Lord more than anything.

00:00:04.600 --> 00:00:05.520
Our home is a small

00:00:05.520 --> 00:00:07.720
50s fixer upper on a little half acre.

00:00:07.720 --> 00:00:08.760
We don't have all that much,

00:00:08.760 --> 00:00:09.960
but we are rich in other ways.

00:00:09.960 --> 00:00:11.720
If this year you wanna learn how to run a home,

00:00:11.720 --> 00:00:12.640
king gardening tips,

00:00:12.640 --> 00:00:13.960
learn from scratch cooking,

00:00:13.960 --> 00:00:15.480
learning how to preserve your harvest.

00:00:15.480 --> 00:00:17.440
And generally be encouraged in the work of the home.

00:00:17.440 --> 00:00:18.971
I would love for us to be friends.
